title: BOOTLEGGER'S DRIVE-IN SATURDAY NIGHT - THE BRAIN & WEREWOLF IN A GIRL'S DORMITORY

sources.title: BOOTLEGGER'S DRIVE-IN SATURDAY NIGHT - THE BRAIN & WEREWOLF IN A GIRL'S DORMITORY
sources.description: A COMPLETE DVD. Zipped folder contains the pre-programed dvd, with the custom menu w/ poster art and audio. Just down load the .zip, open it, extract the VIDEO_TS folder and burn, that's the quickest way. I've also upload the files outside the .zip so they can be viewed here on the site. This disc contains the movies THE BRAIN & WEREWOLF IN A GIRLS DORMITORY, as well as the preview and intermission reels, laid out to play like an old drive-in show.
